<DocsLayout
  title="Express Rate Limit Middleware - hitlimit | Best Express.js Rate Limiter"
  description="Express.js rate limiting middleware with hitlimit. Protect your Express APIs with high-performance rate limiting - route-specific limits, custom keys, Redis/SQLite stores. express-rate-limit alternative."
